ut everything else. And that makes it hard to separate sitting down and writing a post, and fixing a number of other things that go on in a Wordpress install. Also, can we all agree that the WYSIWYG editor in Wordpress is a piece of junk?","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":298,"offset":356},"end":{"line":3,"column":948,"offset":1006}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":2,"column":1,"offset":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":948,"offset":1006}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"While in another rut, I discovered ","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1,"offset":1008},"end":{"line":5,"column":36,"offset":1043}}},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://ghost.org/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Ghost","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":37,"offset":1044},"end":{"line":5,"column":42,"offset":1049}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":36,"offset":1043},"end":{"line":5,"column":46,"offset":1053}}},{"type":"text","value":". I ended up backing the Kickstarter by John O’Nolan. I loved the idea of natively writing in ","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":46,"offset":1053},"end":{"line":5,"column":140,"offset":1147}}},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"http://daringfireball.net/projects/markdown/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Markdown","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":141,"offset":1148},"end":{"line":5,"column":149,"offset":1156}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":140,"offset":1147},"end":{"line":5,"column":153,"offset":1160}}},{"type":"text","value":" and stripping out almost all of the features. I want to write, but I don’t want get caught ","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":153,"offset":1160},"end":{"line":5,"column":245,"offset":1252}}},{"type":"element","tagName":"em","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"not writing","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":246,"offset":1253},"end":{"line":5,"column":257,"offset":1264}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":245,"offset":1252},"end":{"line":5,"column":258,"offset":1265}}},{"type":"text","value":" because I am updating plugins or fingind a better theme. I also ","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":258,"offset":1265},"end":{"line":5,"column":323,"offset":1330}}},{"type":"element","tagName":"em","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"loved","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":324,"offset":1331},"end":{"line":5,"column":329,"offset":1336}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":323,"offset":1330},"end":{"line":5,"column":330,"offset":1337}}},{"type":"text","value":" the idea of using ","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":330,"offset":1337},"end":{"line":5,"column":349,"offset":1356}}},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://nodejs.org/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Node.js","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":350,"offset":1357},"end":{"line":5,"column":357,"offset":1364}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":349,"offset":1356},"end":{"line":5,"column":361,"offset":1368}}},{"type":"text","value":". This got me excited about writing again, so in anticipation of Ghost coming out, I wrote a ton in ","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":361,"offset":1368},"end":{"line":5,"column":461,"offset":1468}}},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://evernote.com/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Evernote","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":462,"offset":1469},"end":{"line":5,"column":470,"offset":1477}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":461,"offset":1468},"end":{"line":5,"column":474,"offset":1481}}},{"type":"text","value":". And when Ghost finally was released to backers, I installed it locally and then on the forst AWS server I could figure out how to run it on.","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":474,"offset":1481},"end":{"line":5,"column":616,"offset":1623}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1,"offset":1008},"end":{"