static blogging platform, I decided the best way learn what it is is to fire up an install and start posting. The worst thing that can happen is I figure out it’s not for me and try another service.","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":388,"offset":3761},"end":{"line":17,"column":682,"offset":4055}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1,"offset":3374},"end":{"line":17,"column":682,"offset":4055}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"So far, (this ","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1,"offset":4057},"end":{"line":19,"column":15,"offset":4071}}},{"type":"element","tagName":"em","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"one post","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":16,"offset":4072},"end":{"line":19,"column":24,"offset":4080}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":15,"offset":4071},"end":{"line":19,"column":25,"offset":4081}}},{"type":"text","value":"!) it seems to be awesome. But we’ll see. I’m excited again. I want to learn more, but not to the fault of ","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":25,"offset":4081},"end":{"line":19,"column":132,"offset":4188}}},{"type":"element","tagName":"em","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"not blogging","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":133,"offset":4189},"end":{"line":19,"column":145,"offset":4201}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":132,"offset":4188},"end":{"line":19,"column":146,"offset":4202}}},{"type":"text","value":". So stay tuned, and I’ll try to share my experieces with you.","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":146,"offset":4202},"end":{"line":19,"column":208,"offset":4264}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1,"offset":4057},"end":{"line":19,"column":208,"offset":4264}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":1,"column":1,"offset":0},"end":{"line":28,"column":1,"offset":4475}}}}